She returned numerous times and always looked for it. On 12 Jan 2021 she took a photo of the bat, which had relocated. This time, the photo showed the bat's wing was open and looked likely to be deceased.; Bat was not rigid and seemed within 24 hours of death, however, organs had begun rotting.
